title: Graco SnugRider Elite Stroller and Car Seat Carrier, Black Hurricane
text: Graco Snugrider Elite Stroller and car Seat Carrier, Black (Hurricane) Stroller in Saint George, UT $50   SpreadMyAd   Includes only the Stroller (the carrier is only for depiction) **However I do have a Graco SnugRide Click Connect 35 Car Seat, that works great with it. I am selling it as well for an additional $65)** Ultra-lightweight aluminum stroller frame is the perfect infant car seat accessory, providing convenience on the go. Works with all Graco infant car seats (including both Classic Connect and Click Connect seats) One-hand, standing fold with automatic storage lock, means no bending necessary. Extra-large storage basket with zippered pocket securely holds your travel essentials. Turns your car seat into an ultra-portable travel solution
